<item>
            <title>[HIVE-13086] LLAP: Programmatically initialize log4j2 to print out the properties location</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-13086</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In some cases, llap daemon gets initialized with different log4j2.properties than the expected llap-daemon-log4j2.properties. It will be easier if programmatically configure log4j2 so that we can print out the location of properties file that is used for initialization. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
